message: Hello! Thank you for contacting Better Deal Insurance. My name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
I'm so frustrated with your company! Your service is terrible!
I'm deeply sorry to hear that you're feeling frustrated. I'm here to help. Before we proceed, can you confirm your full name for security purposes?
Thank you for completing security. Can you also provide your date of birth?
That's all correct. To better assist you, can you please confirm your first line of address and postcode?
Great, thank you for verifying. How can I help you with our service today?
I've had a horrible experience with a recent claim. Your company has not been helpful at all!
I apologize for any inconvenience caused by your recent claim experience. Let's see how we can find a way forward. A possible resolution could be...
I don't want your proposed solution! I want my claim to be processed correctly and promptly!
I completely understand your frustration. Let's work together to find a solution that works best for you. What would be your preference in this situation?
I expect Better Deal Insurance to handle my claim professionally and efficiently without any further delays!
I hear your concerns and value your feedback. Please allow me to see what more we can do to assist you in this matter.
This is unacceptable! I demand better service from your company!

I'm truly sorry to hear that our service has not met your expectations. I will escalate your case to our claims department to ensure this matter is addressed promptly. Is there anything else you would like to add before we conclude?
No, I've said my piece. I hope you improve your services for other customers in the future.
Thank you for sharing your concerns with me. I appreciate your feedback and will ensure it is passed along. You are welcome to reach out anytime if you need further assistance. Have a great day!
